"I hereby being the customer authorize Falcon to charge/ Block any amount(s) for bills generated or unbilled amounts & related expenses on account of telecom
usage to my above mentioned card(s). These expenses are to be charged to my nominated credit card (s) at the sole discretion of Falcon. This instruction is valid
on an ongoing basis. I agree to advise Falcon if my nominated credit card account is cancelled, substituted or not renewed. In such case, I agree to provide
alternative payment instructions as specified by Falcon.
The customer is requested to return the equipment at the same place from where it is taken, falling which, Falcon will charge additional rental.
 "

(*) Prices as per the Tariff Plan/Clay Pack selected will be debited from your credit card as per above declaration. The call charges along with the service charges
and taxes will also be debited to your account on receipt of itemized bill of calls made / received.The above rates are for the destination country only. Roaming rates
will be extra. Toll Free Numbers other than Clay Toll Free Number are Chargeable. All disputes are subject to the jurisdiction of Delhi / New Delhi courts only.

"The above goods have been received by me in excellent working condition and I agree to return the same to Falcon in excellent working condition. I authorize
Falcon to prepare my usage bill as per above rates and charge my credit card account as per details given above. If the amount due is not settled within one week
of the presentation of the bill, I understand that I will be charged on the outstanding amount an interest @ 2% per month. I hereby undertake not to misuse the
mobile phone / SIM card taken from Falcon for any illegal / unauthorized purposes and indemnify Falcon for any legal consequences whatsoever.

This customer agreement form consists of 3 pages and I confirm that I have read the terms and conditions mentioned in both the pages and I agree to abide with
them
 "
"Kindly call on our 24 X 7 Customer Care no. +91.11.66470000 for any Return / Loss of Products information.\n "

"a) All inventory (Handset(s), SIM card(s), data cards(s) given to customers under the agreement must be returned with in 48 hours of expiry of contracted time. In
case of any delay customer would be subjected to a charge of INR 100/ day till its returned to Falconâ€™s Office. Falcon would not be laible for any misuse while the
above inventory is in customers possession.
b) All inventory if not returned to Falcon after expiry of 48 hrs from the contracted period shall be suspended & suspension charges of INR 1000/- will have to be
borne by the client.
c) Calls/ SMS subscribtion to premium services can only be activated or deactivated by the user. The charges to the services do not form the part of normal
contracted rates & will be subjected to premium rates levied by the operator with varied costs.
 "
Falcon Business Resources Pvt. Ltd. hereinafter referred as Falcon & Customer, whose details are given overleaf agree as follows:

1. Falcon would provide customers with mobile phones, SIM cards, data cards, Blackberry connections for short/long term usage at its own discretion, the above would remain sole property of falcon at all times, The same would
have to be returned to Falcon as per the agreement / as demanded by Falcon

The customer will be using various Mobile Phone/Data cards/Blackberry and SIMI Cards provided by Falcon for self-usage and will not transfer them to any third party without explicit written consent and authorization by Falcon.

2. The customer is not permitted to use products provided by the Falcon for any antinational, illegal, unlawful, abusive purposes or for sending obscene, indecent, threatening, harassing, unsolicited messages or messages
